data.description: Discover the allure of Florence, AZ! This captivating home sits on a 1.25-acre lot, complete with a fenced yard and solar panels. With 3 beds, 2 baths, and 1,153 sqft of stylish living space, it offers both comfort and elegance. The open floor plan is perfect for entertaining, while the deck provides stunning mountain views. Ideal for equestrians, the property is horse-ready. Close to amenities, this gem shouldn't be missed. Embrace Florence's beauty and make this your dream home!
